To run the Elastic cluster:
docker-compose -f elastic_stack.yml up

To connect to the cluster via graphical interface:
Visit http://localhost:5601/ using a web browser

To stop the cluster:
docker-compose -f elastic_stack.yml down

The index data generated by Elastic Search is preserved in docker volume.
To delete the data volume while stopping the cluster:
docker-compose -f elastic_stack.yml down -v

